{"tid":970872,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"電競補品實測！打機決戰增勝算","createTime":"2019-01-06T08:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T04:34:43.000Z","uid":127753,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"13a7e23d127a34adb0bb9237d2f025406af33348","tid":970872,"uid":127753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T08:04:57.000Z","msg":"電競熱潮停不了！其實電子競技同很多運動一樣，去到某個Level後成績總是停滯不前。老套講句「工欲善其事，必先利其器」，想增加勝算，專業的電競椅、滑鼠及鍵盤缺一不可，近期仲有電競枱面世。一於請Valkyrie Prime電競女子隊成員Shiro，逐樣試清楚係咪咁好用！<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20190105/photo/0105-00300-001h1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20190105%2Fphoto%2F0105-00300-001h1.jpg&h=2bf4ebef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>桶櫈設計富包圍感</strong><br />\n意大利品牌MomoDesign，出開汽車配件精品，近年攻入電競椅市場，好似新抵港的MD-GC003採用「桶櫈」設計，椅背具一定厚度，頭枕及腰靠符合人體工學，同時可調節高低，Shiro試坐後都話充滿包圍感，而且表面有網眼織物，透氣性高，坐得耐都咁舒服。美中不足是電競椅的後仰幅度不大，比賽中場時難以躺平休息，不過此設計減輕了後翻的可能性，感覺更安全。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>電競枱防滑受力</strong><br />\n至於新推出的MD-GT001打機專用枱，枱面長120cm、闊66cm，基本夠晒位擺放打機用品，可負重達300kg，比坊間不少電腦枱穩陣。至於枱面滿布碳纖維紋理，先天具防滑作用，邊位更設有保護牆以防物件掉落。「Z」形枱腳則可穩固抓地，Shiro笑稱打輸咗發脾氣都難以「翻枱」，可惜其高度限制在75cm，若然有得調低就更啱女玩家使用。<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20190105/photo/0105-00300-001p2g3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20190105%2Fphoto%2F0105-00300-001p2g3.jpg&h=a32135fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20190105/photo/0105-00300-001p3g3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20190105%2Fphoto%2F0105-00300-001p3g3.jpg&h=4ce35ec2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20190105/photo/0105-00300-001p4g3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20190105%2Fphoto%2F0105-00300-001p4g3.jpg&h=ae3f45bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>初音鍵盤滑鼠吸睛</strong><br />\n近年電競界興玩Crossover，新推出的Neptune Elite RGB電競鍵盤便由台灣Tt eSPORTS與日本虛擬偶像初音未來聯乘，腕墊印有初音圖案，代表初音「ミク」兩字的「3」、「9」數字鍵更特別用上代表性的青綠色鍵帽，配合1,680萬色背光燈，夠晒吸睛。軸體是Shiro至愛的青軸，配合鋁製懸浮式鍵帽，反應清脆利落；另有防鬼鍵、巨集記錄、按鍵編程等高階功能。同樣注入初音元素的有Iris RGB電競滑鼠，特設RGB環繞光條及初音圖案，靈敏度達5,000DPI，左右蜂巢紋路具有防滑作用，有姿勢有實際。<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20190105/photo/0105-00300-001p5g4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20190105%2Fphoto%2F0105-00300-001p5g4.jpg&h=4b38279c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20190105/photo/0105-00300-001p6g4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20190105%2Fphoto%2F0105-00300-001p6g4.jpg&h=a00f9c9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20190105/photo/0105-00300-001p7g4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20190105%2Fphoto%2F0105-00300-001p7g4.jpg&h=4fcdf7a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20190105/photo/0105-00300-001p8g5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20190105%2Fphoto%2F0105-00300-001p8g5.jpg&h=726cacb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsource:<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20190105/00300_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20190105%2F00300_001.html&d=X4%2FzfWi5cbJ7qy%2BCoL4PzU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=a0bdc620\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20190105/00300_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係好想同佢瘋狂咁打機呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27cde2129e9a20136b8778bf6ef61e485482438f","tid":970872,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T08:08:46.000Z","msg":"見到第一張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係用人奶提神咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70adef49202c928fde75803ef87c7593cd1f6c6f","tid":970872,"uid":127753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T08:30:57.000Z","msg":"香港有人奶算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好過對住飛機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfbe879f9343d2596feff7415f52ad1b49b8fc7b","tid":970872,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T08:45:53.000Z","msg":"條女ig?"},{"pid":"a63ae5b54f72e1092d97efe3fd17c7ef9e6e2a6b","tid":970872,"uid":53588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T09:27:46.000Z","msg":"女子電莖隊到底有咩鳩野用？<br />\n做雞多個名目？"},{"pid":"bc1978116be9614c704f088079dbfae4fae43411","tid":970872,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T09:43:07.000Z","msg":"咁坐法條腰會好有事"},{"pid":"ccac251963ed86e34ce6960d4db1c30bffbaf445","tid":970872,"uid":135200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T02:17:38.000Z","msg":"買張電競椅係咪送埋條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e424b4575c7f72235d0081680812885dde594d","tid":970872,"uid":33104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccac251963ed86e34ce6960d4db1c30bffbaf445","tid":970872,"uid":135200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T02:17:38.000Z","msg":"買張電競椅係咪送埋條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"r